summary: i have school start again tomorrow and i was just wondering if you could perhaps maybe if u want write a little something about...
question: i have school start again tomorrow and i was just wondering if you could perhaps maybe if u want write a little something about supportive bf harry 🤧🤧🤧
answer:
“bought you pens awhile ago! they’re the better ones. then i compiled some stuff over the weeks. they still do binders, right? or expanding folders? because i bought two of each.”

harry’s gonna babble, pulling things left and right from his bag as he’s gonna sleep overnight at your place and even drive you to school tomorrow, you being all in a huff as you’re going to adjust again to school hours and its load.

“aw, quite being grumpy, bub.”

boyfriend!h really tries to cheer you up, holding your limp figure that’s groaning into the couch right to his chest yet you collapsed to his lap, turning and whining until he stops you.

he chuckles on how you’re acting and he tried this year to not mention the days that are nearing starting a month before you go back — but as he figures, it didn’t make much of a difference at all as you’re still droopy and not bubbly anymore.

“you’re a star student, lovie. g’na be adjusted to it again and before you know it, s’the end of the semester again.”

his words are doing its effect of lightening you up, but the fact that’s still present in your head that you won’t get to relax as often when you’re on break sinks in.

and harry notices it.

he’s quick to press you to his chest, peppering you with kisses from your forehead and to your cheek until his lips pause before pressing to yours.

“after your classes tomorrow, we could do anything you want. anything, alright? sounds good?”
